    "182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--15227346190419__182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d-collapsible_row-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Features",
            "row_content": "{{ product.metafields.custom.specs_features | metafield_tag }}",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15227346190419__182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d-collapsible_row-2": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Satisfaction Guarantee",
            "row_content": "{{ product.metafields.custom.global_text.value.satisfaction_guaranteed | metafield_tag }}",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15227346190419__182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d-collapsible_row-3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Pressing Instructions",
            "row_content": "<p>We recommend watching our step-by-step spangle pressing video tutorial <a href=\"/pages/heat-press-instructions-for-spangle-transfers\" title=\"Heat Press Instructions for Spangle Transfers\">here</a>.</p><p><strong>1. Prepare the Spangle Transfer</strong></p><p>Carefully peel off the transfer's backing, ensuring that only the spangle design remains on the clear adhesive sheet. Handle the transfer gently to prevent shifting or misalignment. Before applying, check that the design is intact and free from dust or debris to ensure a smooth and even press.</p><p><strong>2. Position the Transfer</strong></p><p>Place the transfer adhesive side down onto the garment in your desired location, ensuring it is properly aligned. Smooth out any bubbles or wrinkles to create an even application and prevent lifting during pressing. If necessary, use <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/thermal-heat-tape-1-roll\" title=\"Thermal Heat Tape\">heat-resistant tape</a> to keep the transfer securely in place. Use our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/dtf-alignment-ruler-set\" title=\"DTF Alignment Ruler Set\">Alignment Ruler Set</a> for more precise placement.</p><p><strong>3. Press</strong></p><p>Set the heat press to 300°F - 315°F, and apply medium to firm pressure for 12-15 seconds. If you're using our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/ninjaflex-heat-press-garment-protector\" title=\"Silicone Upper Platen Cover & Garment Protector\">Silicone Upper Platen Cover</a>, set your heat press to 330°F.</p><p><strong>4. Peel the Transfer</strong></p><p>Allow the garment to sit for 15-30 seconds, giving the adhesive time to set. Then, carefully peel the carrier sheet while it is still warm, using a smooth and steady motion to prevent lifting. After peeling, inspect the design to ensure all spangles have adhered properly for a flawless finish.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "template--15227346190419__182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d-collapsible_row-4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "row_content": "<p>All Spangle orders ships in 6 business days. Orders over $75 will automatically qualify for <strong>Free Shipping</strong>. </p><p>Read our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/shipping-policy\">Shipping Policy</a> for more information.</p><p><strong>Refunds & Reprints</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/pages/contact\" target=\"_blank\">Contact us</a> within 45 days of receiving your order to submit a request for a refund or reprint. We will reprint any order where there is a print quality or adherence issue. However, we will not issue a reprint if the uploaded file is low quality. If you'd like a refund or reprint for another reason, it must be approved by management first.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "3bc27b13-267d-4bef-a809-08d207429433": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Art Upload Recommendations",
            "row_content": "{{ product.metafields.custom.global_text.value.art | metafield_tag }}",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_tem7Hj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Build Your Own DTF Transfer",
            "row_content": "<p>Don't have your own design, now you can create your own transfers with our <a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/ninja-dtf-transfer-builder\" target=\"_blank\">Ninja DTF Transfer Builder</a>.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "338f1c7b-8d49-4684-b836-c21b53dd7834": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Glitter Option",
            "row_content": "<p>Looking to brighten up your designs and make them stand out even more? Glitter is available if you choose our Gang Sheet Builder Option.</p><p><a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/build-your-own-gang-sheet?variant=41169746067539\" title=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/build-your-own-gang-sheet?variant=41169746067539\">Build Your Glitter Gang Sheet Here</a></p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_hcCcy4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Custom Numbers",
            "row_content": "<p>Elevate your apparel game with our Custom Numbers DTF Transfer Packs. Each pack includes ten high-quality numbers (0-9), available in two classic fonts: Collegiate and Interstate. Whether you're looking to personalize jerseys, shirts, jackets, or other garments, these versatile numbers are the perfect solution. Choose between left chest sizing (4 inches in height) or a full front design (8 inches in height) to achieve the perfect look.</p><p><a href=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/custom-number-pack\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://ninjatransfers.com/products/custom-number-pack\">Order Them Here</a></p>",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "template--15227346190419__182b897c-36bd-4159-8101-be4189eb919d-collapsible_row-1",
